{"comments":"Color Token molecule.\n\nA ColorToken binds a semantic name to a color value. This enables\nagents to reference colors by meaning rather than value.\n\n## Structure\n\n```\nColorToken = TokenMeta + OKLCH + ColorRole\n```\n\n## Examples\n\n```purescript\nprimaryToken :: ColorToken\nprimaryToken = mkColorToken\n  (TokenName \"color.primary.500\")\n  (TokenDesc \"Primary brand color for interactive elements\")\n  (oklch 0.65 0.24 240.0)  -- Vivid blue\n  RolePrimary\n```\n\n## Color Roles\n\nColors have semantic roles that define their purpose:\n- **Primary**: Main brand color, interactive elements\n- **Secondary**: Supporting brand color\n- **Accent**: Highlights, calls to action\n- **Neutral**: Grays for text, borders, backgrounds\n- **Success/Warning/Error/Info**: Semantic feedback colors\n\n## At Billion-Agent Scale\n\nWhen agents compose UI, they reference `color.primary.500` rather than\na specific OKLCH value. The token system resolves references at render\ntime, enabling theme switching, dark mode, and brand customization\nwithout changing component code.\n","declarations":[{"children":[],"comments":"Color design token.\n\nBinds a semantic name to an OKLCH color value with role metadata.\n\n## Invariants\n\n- Name follows token naming conventions\n- Value is a valid OKLCH color\n- Role matches the intended usage\n","info":{"arguments":[],"declType":"typeSynonym","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Record"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["meta",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Brand","Token"],"TokenMeta"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["value",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","OKLCH"],"OKLCH"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":["role",{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Brand","Token","Color"],"ColorRole"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"tag":"REmpty"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"RCons"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[300,4],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Brand/Token/Color.purs","start":[296,1]},"title":"ColorToken"},{"children":[],"comments":"Create a color token with full metadata.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Brand","Token"],"TokenName"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Brand","Token"],"TokenDesc"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Color","OKLCH"],"OKLCH"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Brand","Token","Color"],"ColorRole"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Brand","Token","Color"],"ColorToken"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}],"tag":"TypeApp"}},"kind":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[303,75],"name":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/Schema/Brand/Token/Color.purs","start":[303,1]},"title":"mkColorToken"},{"children":[],"comments":"Create a color token with minimal metadata.\n\nDescription is derived from the token name.\n","info":{"declType":"value","type":{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Prim"],"Function"],"tag":"TypeConstructor"},{"annotation":[],"contents":[["Hydrogen","Schema","Brand"